{"tid":1207521,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"環球時報：內地社會比任何外部勢力更盼望香港好","createTime":"2019-06-12T06:49:10.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-12T07:04:09.000Z","uid":48093,"like":2,"dislike":22,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"b093f0a4cb155e5975d252c63fabfdc2590e41fe","tid":1207521,"uid":48093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T06:49:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://newsstatic.rthk.hk/images/mfile_1462339_1_L_20190612144119.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnewsstatic.rthk.hk%2Fimages%2Fmfile_1462339_1_L_20190612144119.jpg&h=37ee6a38&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n內地《環球時報》總編輯胡錫進以筆名「單仁平」發表評論員文章，指出內地社會比任何外部勢力更盼望香港好。一旦香港社會大亂，損失最大的將是香港市民，而最心疼也最無奈的將是中華民族這個利益共同體。<br />\n<br />\n文章批評，香港反對派不斷宣揚北京要打壓香港社會的基本價值，包括法治和自由，想把香港變得和內地一樣，改變香港人的現有生活方式。這種說法不僅與「一國兩制」的基本精神南轅北轍，也與內地社會的對港心理嚴重不符。<br />\n<br />\n文章又說，台灣當局巴不得香港衰落，以證明它「拒絕統一」是正確的，而美國最關心是如何用香港事務找中國的麻煩。"},{"pid":"2f01e6f318c89414d8de975515d79821ffb7f7a8","tid":1207521,"uid":29080,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T06:50:44.000Z","msg":"閱👌"},{"pid":"15b709592c44e6d0bf04ca358f21a91bbd9cd8f8","tid":1207521,"uid":143078,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T06:51:48.000Z","msg":"noted with thanks!! <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1811522153fe98814eac8e6cd3f6060612e97490","tid":1207521,"uid":66049,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T06:52:57.000Z","msg":"收皮啦"},{"pid":"50b4bdcba469c4ad501773e681c8ac5cc1cbe5c2","tid":1207521,"uid":130406,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T06:55:55.000Z","msg":"[想衝但又怕嘅入嚟] 各種分工 衝要用腦有陣形<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/cKPROT\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/cKPROT</a>"},{"pid":"7e933ea0d75bb90fd4cdc302a0e40dc8fc98babc","tid":1207521,"uid":28279,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T07:00:14.000Z","msg":"解散你個傀儡港共政府先講<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/34.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1832319730ae986fffb4e984a2e3e652973c011d","tid":1207521,"uid":29625,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T07:00:33.000Z","msg":"Well noted."},{"pid":"154a6f9859893b4e4f3a25d3b849b812944e9742","tid":1207521,"uid":55913,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T07:03:26.000Z","msg":"屌你老味死開啦"},{"pid":"4989c8b87e39db468fab618c3a0b3addf02839c7","tid":1207521,"uid":226972,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T07:04:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Xq9kTXF.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXq9kTXF.png&h=37e1dfb3&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}